\]

3. From \( B_3 = 44 \):
\[ B_4 = 
\begin{cases} 
3 \cdot 44 - 1 = 131 & \text{with probability } \frac{1}{2} \\
44 + 1 = 45 & \text{with probability } \frac{1}{2}
